In 2012, a very large collection of artists came together to bring club banger megahit BALLOON PARTY: 100% NO FEEBLE CHEERING and shocked the music production scene with the sheer force of just one little pink horse's ability to party hard.

MLR brings you RAINBOW & ROOTED: FOUR'S FALL DOWN, the Rainbow Dash part of the series of pony megahit albums. This year, have your ears taken by storm by the wild and restless spirit of music, daring to put forth hi-fi and lo-fi music alike, ranging from ragged punk rock to crisp drum and bass. This album defines the wild side of this fandom's musical prowess, and a loyal stance is taken by every one of these awesome tracks.
